01:10:42.898 --> 01:11:06.277
Incoming livestream: So that brings me to my motivation for today, which is agent evaluation today is rooted in very narrow, outcome-only scoring, which essentially hides explainability and reliability. So, if you have an agent, it achieves 80% success on a benchmark, that doesn't tell you much, right? That doesn't tell you why it worked 80% of the time. It doesn't tell you why it failed the other 20% of the time.


