01:13:47.278 --> 01:14:10.078
Incoming livestream: And to solve for that, we built Clasp. So CLASP is a capability-centric evaluation framework. The idea is very simple. It gives you 6 rubrics for six different agentic capabilities. And the idea is that if the agent has a very brittle capability, then you get a lower score. If it has a very adaptive execution of the same capability, you get a higher score.


